                <head>220. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee (Intelligence)
                        Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d220fn1">Source: National Security
                        Council, <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> Administration
                        Intelligence Files, Box I–020, Minutes—<gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss>
                        1980. Secret; Sensitive. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName>
